FBIS4-37171 "drnes117_r_94005" FBIS-NES-94-117 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 SOUTH ASIA India 6 Killed in Kashmir Valley 6 Killed in Kashmir Valley BK1606155994 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 16 Jun 94 BK1606155994 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] In Kashmir Valley, six persons, including four militants, were killed in the last 24 hours. An official spokesman said in Srinagar today that the security forces arrested 39 militants, including five hard-core, and recovered a large quantity of arms and ammunition. Meanwhile, the day curfew was lifted in Bhadarwah town of Doda District today following improvement in the situation. Night curfew from 1900 till 0700 will however continue as a precautionary measure.
